2. Project: Vending Machine Monitoring Web Station 

. In this Project, we mock up a smart vending machine system,use android to develop the vending machine client side, and I primarily focusing on the monitor system.For the web-based monitor subsystem, we have used Bootstrap, JQuery, EJS template for front-end. NodeJs, ExpressJs for back-end.

What is the function of Monitoring web site?
1. For example it is able to get all the statistics, including items, machine and sales info of the whole system, and modify all the information if necessary.

2. Also allow employees to register and login, the employees work on each vending machine to register the machine, add or delete item to or from machine and refill machine when needed.

3.  Each vending machine itself has a background process going on periodically to synchronize the local database with the central database.

3.About work 

In this work, I am a student research assistant, focusing on the existing remote authentication scheme based on biological characteristics, like fring print and palmprint, and analyzed the safety defects in the scheme, then develop a new blind identity authentication scheme based on palmprint  The scheme can effectively solve issues on user privacy, template protection and trust.
